<div class="container">
  <div class="row mt-4 text-left">
      <h4>退会手続き</h4>
      <hr class="hr1">
  </div>


<div class="container">
    <div class="row mt-5 justify-content-center">
      <i class="fa-solid fa-triangle-exclamation fa-3x "style="color: gold;" ></i>
    </div>
    <div class="row mt-5 justify-content-center">
      <h4><font color="#ff0000">退会手続き前にご確認ください</font></h4>
    </div>

    <div class="row mt-5 justify-content-center text-center">
      <h5>退会された場合、注文履歴や配送先など登録した情報が
      <font color="#ff0000">すべて削除されます。</font><br>
      よろしければ下記の「退会する」ボタンで退会手続きできます。</h5>
    </div>

<% if customer_signed_in? %>
<div class="row mt-5 mb-5 justify-content-center">
  <div class="col-2 text-center">
  <%= link_to "退会する", public_withdraw_user_path(@customer), method: :patch, class: "btn btn-sm btn-danger", "data-confirm" => "本当に退会しますか？" %>
  </div>
  <div class="col-2 text-center">
  <%= link_to "退会しない", public_customers_path, class: "btn btn-sm btn-primary" %>
  </div>
</div>
<% end %>

<% if general_customer_signed_in? %>
<div class="row mt-5 mb-5 justify-content-center">
  <div class="col-2 text-center">
  <%= link_to "退会する", general_public_withdraw_user_path(@general_customer), method: :patch, class: "btn btn-sm btn-danger", "data-confirm" => "本当に退会しますか？" %>
  </div>
  <div class="col-2 text-center">
  <%= link_to "退会しない", general_public_customers_path, class: "btn btn-sm btn-primary" %>
  </div>
</div>
<% end %>


</div>
</div>



